        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Zero / Round / Copy / Paste </text>shortcut menu </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Right-click a parameter&apos;s data-value to see this shortcut menu.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Zero</text> - make the data-value equal zero - if possible</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Round</text> - make the data-value exactly divisible by the Spin-Increment</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Copy</text> - copy the data-value to the Clipboard</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Paste</text> - replace data-value with value in Clipboard</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
